ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAGREEMENT - Bring into force Costa Rica FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the REPUBLIC OF COSTA RICA FOR THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS, signed on 11 August 2011.
